name: Revo Uninstaller Pro Log
summary: Learn about .RUEL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: To export a log, right-click the program from the "New Programs" or "Other Programs" lists and select "Export Log."
NOTE: You can import RUEL log files created by other users and operate the log as if you created it and have traced the installation of the specific program yourself.

description: Exported log in the Ruel format created and used by Revo Uninstaller Pro, a program that helps users uninstall programs; contains log data for a program; includes information about properties, registry items, and files and folders.
